title: Bills-Rams Preview + Go Get My Lunch!
itunes:title: Bills-Rams Preview + Go Get My Lunch!
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Colleen Wolfe bring you all the latest news around the league, starting with Mitchell Trubisky being named the starter for the Steelers (7:26). We have some fun with Trubisky poking fun at Russell Wilson's "Let's Ride" video before looking ahead to the start of the NFL season with Week 1's matchup between the Rams and the Bills (16:15). Finally, it's the 2022 edition of "Go Get My Lunch" (33:00).

Note: timecodes approximate
